This page is dedicated to the various cultures of VRChat. A [[wikipedia:Culture|culture]] is a dynamic abstraction or concept, of '''common or shared groups''' of interests, activities, or social behaviors and norms among a community or population. An easier way to understanding VRChat culture, is by interacting with other users through observation or kinesthetically participating in healthy mutual activities on the platform. Some users have even created [[groups]] to find others who may share a similar pre-existing culture or idea. Users on VRChat may also use or create lingo or [[Special:MyLanguage/Community:Terminology|terminology]], based on ideas associated with VRChat.

